{"tid":1905163,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"既然黃色YouTube圈已經開始成型 有冇人可以整個list自己loop比佢地賺廣告費？","createTime":"2020-03-01T05:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T09:54:06.000Z","uid":97114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58e087a016ee90fa990c80d0528768c44e6c5061","tid":1905163,"uid":97114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到happy kongner 新片講一般youtuber既Google廣告收入 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/p-GzO8Jem_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp-GzO8Jem_w&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGov7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=3e091106\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p-GzO8Jem_w</a><br />\n幾萬views可能都係得2，300USD <br />\n但每一條片都要幾十個鐘既功夫<br />\n計起黎有時每粒鐘真係得幾蚊港紙收入...<br />\n仲要而家成日都黃標 好多片都無廣告收入<br />\n<br />\n所以有冇人可以同各youtuber合作 group埋一堆有潛力既片去整一個list 等一般人可以放個電腦係到掛機賺錢（其實之前都有人提出 但好似不了了之 今次黃色youtuber出晒黎 順便可以上埋熱門等更多人睇到 做埋宣傳既效果"},{"pid":"3666e6f42f6413aef9da909ca0211ce3915ca855","tid":1905163,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"上網睇list係刷唔到點擊率<br />\n可以search 打榜方法研究下"},{"pid":"fb9a5d60fa3879614a1d172b1b6a1c08a54ba3eb","tid":1905163,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"可以寫個script loop"},{"pid":"efd4d0bc7df0e61e31c3631cd5b88d79d8748967","tid":1905163,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb9a5d60fa3879614a1d172b1b6a1c08a54ba3eb","tid":1905163,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"可以寫個script loop"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptpOAtf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptpOAtf.png&h=13482237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知點解插代碼reply唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ea2e579b2132459b599d794b4aca02e84be1ec","tid":1905163,"uid":46950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s